ai-patthana17.29:0.2_0: (This should be expanded as in the teachings.)
ai-patthana17.29:0.3_0: These are the result of past deeds, self-mortification, and the result of deeds.
ai-patthana17.29:1.1_0: The result of unsuitable teaching doesn’t lead to the result of past deeds.
ai-patthana17.29:2.1_0: There is no such thing as a result of past deeds.
ai-patthana17.29:3.1_0: There is no such thing as the result of deeds.
